#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "Installing Java SDK"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "Java SDK is required by Vaadin and also by the Eclipse IDE. Vaadin is compatible with Java 1.6 and later editions. Java EE 7 is required for proper server push support with WebSockets."
