#, no-c-format
msgid "You can download the newest Vaadin installation package from the download page at <link xlink:href=\"http://vaadin.com/download/\">http://vaadin.com/download/</link>. Please use a ZIP decompression utility available in your operating system to extract the files from the ZIP package."
